text: Blackpink is the group that can cheer you up at a difficult moment. They are not worthy of a hate. Rose is the person who will help in any situation, she doesn’t care about money and then I would call her the queen of love. Lisa is the person who makes you go to the goal and  don’t give up. Jennie is the person who withstood a lot of hate but didn’t give up, she taught me that you don’t need to listen to others, but you need to think for yourself. Jisoo is a person who always has a smile on his face. I learned from Jisoo that you need to be cheerful and  positive (she taught me a lot but I can’t say everything) BLACKPINK is a group that has always been loved and will remain so. All members in the group are the best in their own way if a person is a real fan of them, he will understand all this. Having written all this, I want to say that people stop  to hate some of them I want to answer: Jennie is said that she is lazy but if she was like that she would not have achieved such popularity. Jisoo is told that she is not beautiful and did not know that she is the most beautiful girl in Korea.Lisa having hate for being Thai but a real person should not be judged by nationality.  Rose is hated because she doesn't have vocals but at the same time not knowing that Rose has the best voice in Korea. The girls have achieved subtle success for a reason, they deserve it. All Blinks will understand these glory. Please stop hating them. I understand that they  they will leave soon and will not sing as before.
